  <name>CKDEPS</name>
  <summary>Beautiful CachyOS system deployment wizard</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      CKDEPS transforms your CachyOS fresh-install experience into a beautiful,
      guided wizard. Select packages from AUR and Flatpak, configure system extras, and
      watch everything install with live progress tracking — all from a stunning GUI.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>One-click system bootstrap (pacman update, yay, flatpak setup)</li>
      <li>Beautiful package selection grid with install status detection</li>
      <li>AUR and Flatpak package support</li>
      <li>System configuration extras (aliases, Hyprland startup, GNOME privacy)</li>
      <li>Live installation progress with real-time log output</li>
      <li>Comprehensive deployment summary</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  <launchable type="desktop-id">com.goodborn.ckdeps.desktop</launchable>
  <url type="homepage">https://github.com.goodborn.ckdeps-deploy</url>
  <url type="bugtracker">https://github.com.goodborn.ckdeps-deploy/issues</url>
